	* src/rbgobj_type.c: use rbgobj_init_object_class() to initialize
	object class.
	* src/rbgobj_object.c, src/global.h: add new function
	rbgobj_init_object_class().

	* src/rbgobj_object.c (rbgobj_gobject_new): check returned value of
	g_object_newv().

